Ok. The Pirate Bay has now gone to the "Magnet Torrent" system for 99% of the uploads. So, if you are using uTorrent or Vuze and you have clicked on the "Get This Torrent" link next to the magnet and it does not start downloading, you may need to update your bit torrent protocol, so that it opens it for you. Hope this helps :)
